        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Usage</strong> affixed to a weapon</p>\n<p><strong>Activation</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">F</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You damage a creature that is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} with a Strike using the affixed weapon</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are an expert with the affixed weapon.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This repulsive, hairy glob dangles from the end of your weapon. When you activate the putrescent glob, the creature you damaged must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:23] save or its sickened condition increases to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2}, and it can't reduce its sickened condition until the end of its next turn. On a critical failure, it's also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} until the end of its next turn.</p>"
